item.title: Game for boys for 10 years
item.description: A game for boys for 10 years old invites you to go on an exciting duck hunt. By controlling the movements of the sight with the arrow keys on the keyboard, try to shoot as many ducks as possible. Demonstrate your reaction and eye and score the maximum number of points in this exciting shooter.
